description: Looking for an easy dinner recipe? This creamy chicken alfredo made using fettuccine, BBQ roast chicken and zucchini ribbons is a guaranteed winner.
name: Speedy Cheesy Chicken & Zucchini Alfredo Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs Woolworths extra virgin olive oil
250 ml tub Philadelphia light cooking cream

recipeInstructions.text: Add pasta, chicken meat and reserved cooking liquid to pan. Reduce heat to low and toss for 2 minutes or until heated through. Serve topped with zucchini ribbons, stuffing, parsley leaves and parmesan.
